title: LEGO Little Elf Helpers & Santa Sets Only $4.99 Each (Regularly $9.99)
text: Grab these LEGO Sets NOW and Stash Away for next Christmas! Head on over to LEGO.com where they are offering up this LEGO Little Elf Helpers Set and/or this LEGO Santa Set for only $4.99 each (regularly $9.99).
